data.name: TextBox1.Value
data.value: A positive result is provided for bacteria, virus, parasites, and/or fungal species when PCR amplification (real-time PCR), sequence information (Pyrosequencing), and/or sequencing analysis occurs above cut-off levels established by the laboratory. Pertinent reference intervals for the tests reported above are available from the laboratory upon request.

data.name: TextBox2.Value
data.value: *This test was developed and its performance characteristics determined by the laboratory. It has not been cleared or approved by the U.S. Food and Drug Administration. The FDA has determined that such clearance or approval is not necessary.
